268
00:18:54,967 --> 00:18:57,162
You're starting to make me
a little nervous.

269
00:18:57,336 --> 00:18:59,736
Why am I
starting to make you nervous?

270
00:19:01,206 --> 00:19:04,539
Because I'm starting to think you
might be too good of a person for me.

271
00:19:04,710 --> 00:19:06,803
No, I'm not that good of a person.

272
00:19:06,979 --> 00:19:11,973
You're sneaking off every day to do
manual labor on a house for charity.

273
00:19:12,151 --> 00:19:15,086
- On your spring break.
- Yeah, you're right.

274
00:19:15,254 --> 00:19:18,849
It's selfish, really,
me being this generous.

275
00:19:19,858 --> 00:19:23,521
- You don't drink, you don't smoke.
- Nope. Nope.

276
00:19:24,663 --> 00:19:27,257
- You probably don't sleep around.
- Absolutely not.

277
00:19:29,134 --> 00:19:30,931
Okay, look, you gotta have a fault.

278
00:19:31,103 --> 00:19:35,005
- I do.
- Okay, care to enlighten me?

279
00:19:37,509 --> 00:19:38,908
I curse.

280
00:19:40,212 --> 00:19:41,440
- No.
- I do.

281
00:19:41,613 --> 00:19:42,671
- No, you don't.
- I do.

282
00:19:42,848 --> 00:19:47,114
- I haven't heard you.
- Well, that's because it's in my mind.

283
00:19:47,753 --> 00:19:50,187
