286
00:19:54,426 --> 00:19:56,451
No, I can't tell you because it's filthy.

287
00:19:56,628 --> 00:19:58,357
- Right.
- Yeah.

288
00:19:58,530 --> 00:20:00,623
Okay, all right. Fair enough.

289
00:20:00,799 --> 00:20:02,790
No, I have faults, John.

290
00:20:02,968 --> 00:20:06,404
Trust me, I have plenty of them.
You'll see.

291
00:20:06,972 --> 00:20:08,462
I hope so.

292
00:20:10,642 --> 00:20:12,906
We have to be finished
with this in three weeks.

293
00:20:13,078 --> 00:20:14,670
Hope that actually happens.

294
00:20:14,846 --> 00:20:16,939
These are to be the bedrooms,
parents' room...

295
00:20:17,115 --> 00:20:20,278
...the boys' rooms,
two boys, 7 and 9.

296
00:20:20,452 --> 00:20:22,352
Living room and the bathroom.

297
00:20:22,521 --> 00:20:24,716
And then this is the kitchen.

298
00:20:24,890 --> 00:20:27,586
This is the best room because
the mom's a really good cook.

299
00:20:27,759 --> 00:20:33,288
