300
00:20:33,465 --> 00:20:37,367
...on the countertops
and there's gonna be a roof.

301
00:20:37,536 --> 00:20:40,869
- Here, John, come here.
- A roof would definitely be good.

302
00:20:42,941 --> 00:20:45,637
It's gonna be like this,
but it's gonna be everywhere.

303
00:20:45,811 --> 00:20:47,369
It's the only cover we have.

304
00:20:47,546 --> 00:20:50,106
Nice, we're gonna be here
for a while.

305
00:20:51,583 --> 00:20:53,483
Where'd you get your scar?

306
00:20:54,286 --> 00:20:55,776
That one?

307
00:20:59,458 --> 00:21:01,085
A knife fight.

308
00:21:01,893 --> 00:21:05,852
It was five years ago, we were really
drunk and the guy went for my eye.

309
00:21:06,031 --> 00:21:07,259
That's terrible.

310
00:21:08,066 --> 00:21:09,966
Why? He missed.

311
00:21:11,837 --> 00:21:16,331
The way people act around you, the
way they treated you at that restaurant.

312
00:21:16,808 --> 00:21:20,300
- It's like they're scared of you.
- They're not scared of me.

313
00:21:21,580 --> 00:21:23,445
They might be scared
of who I used to be.

314
00:21:23,615 --> 00:21:25,344
And who is that?

315
00:21:27,686 --> 00:21:28,880
Somebody different?

316
00:21:29,688 --> 00:21:32,680
So when did you change?
When you went into the Army?

317
00:21:33,725 --> 00:21:36,694
Yeah. Yeah, I mean, partly yeah.

318
00:21:36,862 --> 00:21:38,159
And the other part?

319
00:21:39,197 --> 00:21:41,256
I don't know,
I'm still working on that.

320
00:21:43,802 --> 00:21:45,463
So you used to be tough.

321
00:21:47,105 --> 00:21:49,835
And maybe you still are a little bit.

322
00:21:50,008 --> 00:21:52,909
- You don't scare me, John.
- No?

323
00:21:55,013 --> 00:21:56,913
Well, you scare me.

324
00:24:04,976 --> 00:24:06,307
Don't worry about him.

325
00:24:17,189 --> 00:24:18,747
John!

326
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:31,494
What, you think you're safe
in there? Okay.

327
00:24:36,041 --> 00:24:37,872
No!

328
00:25:04,402 --> 00:25:06,700
It's all right.
Everybody understands.

329
00:25:35,667 --> 00:25:37,601
What are you doing over here?

330
00:25:38,837 --> 00:25:40,134
You're missing the party.

331
00:25:40,305 --> 00:25:43,297
The party's just managing fine
without me.

332
00:25:43,842 --> 00:25:45,332
What's wrong?

333
00:25:46,611 --> 00:25:49,079
Why are you all the way
over here by yourself?

334
00:25:49,915 --> 00:25:51,815
