382
00:28:58,002 --> 00:28:59,993
- Now's not a good time, all right?
- You sad?

383
00:29:00,171 --> 00:29:03,436
No, come on. You just need to relax.
Come on. Just relax a little bit.

384
00:29:03,608 --> 00:29:05,303
What's going on with Savannah?

385
00:29:05,477 --> 00:29:07,502
- Just leave me alone.
- What's with Savannah?

386
00:29:07,679 --> 00:29:10,011
- How about you get your hands off?
- Come on.

387
00:29:10,181 --> 00:29:12,240
What is happening
with you and Savannah...?

388
00:29:12,417 --> 00:29:13,850
Hey, man, what are you doing?

389
00:29:14,385 --> 00:29:15,682
John!

390
00:29:16,154 --> 00:29:17,917
Oh, my... Oh, my God!

391
00:29:18,656 --> 00:29:21,648
- John!
- Stop him. What is he doing?

392
00:29:25,130 --> 00:29:28,299
- Help him!
- Oh, I'm so sorry.

393
00:29:54,125 --> 00:29:56,593
I don't think she's home now.

394
00:29:56,761 --> 00:29:59,321
But she hasn't
gone back to school yet.

395
00:30:01,466 --> 00:30:06,062
She normally comes by and says
goodbye before she heads back, but...

396
00:30:10,074 --> 00:30:12,474
Oh, shit, Tim.

397
00:30:12,644 --> 00:30:14,339
Jesus, I'm sorry, man.

398
00:30:14,512 --> 00:30:17,504
Hey, I like it.

399
00:30:17,682 --> 00:30:19,582
I think it makes me look
pretty tough.

400
00:30:20,151 --> 00:30:23,314
I just... I had no idea
it was you back there.

401
00:30:23,888 --> 00:30:25,515
Hey, it was my fault.

402
00:30:25,690 --> 00:30:29,148
I don't know what I was thinking,
sneaking up behind a green beret.

403
00:30:29,327 --> 00:30:31,318
Hey, if you see her...

404
00:30:32,931 --> 00:30:34,694
...can you give her a message
for me?

405
00:30:34,866 --> 00:30:36,333
Yeah.

406
00:30:37,435 --> 00:30:40,461
Just tell her I came by...

407
00:30:41,372 --> 00:30:42,896
...and that I...

408
00:30:43,074 --> 00:30:44,405
You wanna write it down?

409
00:30:47,111 --> 00:30:48,601
Yeah.

410
00:30:51,783 --> 00:30:54,013
I'll make sure she gets it.

411
00:30:54,185 --> 00:30:55,584
Thank you.

412
00:31:07,332 --> 00:31:08,890
Hey, Pop.

413
00:31:10,168 --> 00:31:12,227
I didn't know if anyone
else was coming so...

414
00:31:13,371 --> 00:31:15,430
...I made double.

415
00:31:34,926 --> 00:31:36,416
No, I'll do it.

416
00:31:36,594 --> 00:31:39,028
- I got it, Dad. It's okay. I got it.
- No, I'll do it.

417
00:31:39,197 --> 00:31:41,290
- They're clean.
- I'll do it. I'll do it.

418
00:31:43,368 --> 00:31:44,699
Okay.

419
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:08,150
Looks like you're gonna have
leftovers for once.

420
00:32:09,527 --> 00:32:12,325
Oh, I'll have it next Sunday.

421
00:32:29,881 --> 00:32:31,314
Excuse me, Pop.

