00:32:38,456 --> 00:32:40,356
Got your note.

423
00:32:41,659 --> 00:32:43,854
- Short, sweet, to the point.
- I'm sorry.

424
00:32:44,028 --> 00:32:45,495
John, I'm sorry.

425
00:32:46,097 --> 00:32:48,793
- I'm so sorry.
- No, I'm sorry.

426
00:32:48,967 --> 00:32:50,696
I didn't mean to make you feel that.

427
00:32:50,868 --> 00:32:54,360
I have no idea what I'm talking about.
No business pretending I'm a doctor.

428
00:32:54,539 --> 00:32:56,734
- I was watching him today.
- John.

429
00:32:56,908 --> 00:32:59,604
