00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:31,029
<i>This dream.</i>

520
00:39:32,203 --> 00:39:34,967
<i>I wanna open up</i>
<i>a summer camp for autistic kids.</i>

521
00:39:35,139 --> 00:39:37,073
I've never seen him
