on Monday, then we'll do it.

636
00:47:08,892 --> 00:47:10,257
Together.

637
00:47:14,164 --> 00:47:15,825
Don't get into trouble over there.

638
00:47:15,999 --> 00:47:17,933
- Take care of yourself.
- Always.

639
00:47:18,101 --> 00:47:20,661
