648
00:47:38,288 --> 00:47:40,381
I don't know when
I'll get that again...

649
00:47:40,557 --> 00:47:42,149
...so I gotta go.

650
00:47:42,326 --> 00:47:44,055
Nothing I can say
to change your mind?

651
00:47:44,228 --> 00:47:45,495
Nope.

652
00:47:54,671 --> 00:47:56,195
John!

